features.name: Toxin_YhaV acts as a transcription factor. The YhaV PrlF complex binds the prlF-yhaV operon, probably negatively regulating its expression

PrlF_antitoxin Antitoxin component of a type II toxin-antitoxin (TA) system. Labile antitoxin that binds to the YhaV toxin and neutralizes its ribonuclease activity. Also acts as a transcription factor. The YhaV PrlF complex binds the prlF-yhaV operon, probably negatively regulating its expression
